{"tid":755934,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"完全諗唔明表姐對依個世界有咩價值","createTime":"2018-07-25T15:13:01.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-26T00:15:04.000Z","uid":8371,"like":6,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"af72e7805bec0bce5cda070e98257d5fc470ff4c","tid":755934,"uid":8371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T15:13:01.000Z","msg":"交代翻少少先，表姐一家住係隔離附近<br />\n表姐佢已經25歲人，冇一份工做長過3個月<br />\n份工做一排唔係話人排斥佢，就係太辛苦<br />\n唔好話男朋友，連朋友都肯定冇<br />\n一日到黑淨係識整埋啲咩手作仔，得個幾個客仔又整一大堆<br />\n成日走去讀埋啲唔知咩課程，例如讀左個營養師證書就係度扮代表，拎住份死人note就話我地食嘅野唔健康，嘈住哂，自己又係度食杯麵喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢係安份守己都冇問題，問題係日日係度發脾氣，全家都得罪佢咁，當個世界係圍住佢轉<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔好話貢獻，我完全諗唔到佢生存係度有咩價值<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc6a881bea236949fdc5919c35b1dd9361031a00","tid":755934,"uid":134554,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T15:17:41.000Z","msg":"訓練你EQ同忍耐能力?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f8678def4ae7e123a0546c57a4b1f4997447d43","tid":755934,"uid":1067,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T15:24:09.000Z","msg":"有張八達通就得"},{"pid":"88ff5bce663f02eed348025a8ed763a87136b733","tid":755934,"uid":12628,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T15:27:19.000Z","msg":"想屌你表姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"291774ab303b27532c1fa2e31c860e184b98ae5e","tid":755934,"uid":171816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T15:31:52.000Z","msg":"有冇圖"},{"pid":"7eb90612676fe324d49d9770f3149863f130e5fa","tid":755934,"uid":8371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cc6a881bea236949fdc5919c35b1dd9361031a00","tid":755934,"uid":134554,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T15:17:41.000Z","msg":"訓練你EQ同忍耐能力?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /